nodes.text: Amy Beth Christenson is a senior concept designer at Lucasfilm Animation. She worked as a concept artist for the video games Star Wars: The Force Unleashed and Star Wars: The Force Unleashed II, Topps trading cards, and other things. In 2011, she started working on Star Wars: The Clone Wars also as a concept artist, designing concepts for the Pyke species and the Pyke blaster for the episode "Eminence."
